title: S16 Ep37: Secrets of the Sandsquatch with Boogs
itunes:title: Secrets of the Sandsquatch with Boogs
description:
Darkness Radio presents Secrets of the Sandsquatch with Boogs

Dave & Tim welcome April with an introduction to a little known faction of the Cryptid world, the elusive but ever present Sandsquatch & The White Sands Dunesquatch. What are these creatures and where do they come from? Tune in today and have your world rocked as we unveil the secrets of cryptids and what may have come from Uranus.

Happy April 1st from your pals at Darkness Radio.

Check out Boogs and The Sandsquatch Report Here: www.kingdomofnyeradio.com
